document_data.name: One-Eyed Naerdurr
document_data.mainbody: '''One-Eyed Naerdurr''' was a one-eyed trader of whatever goods he could get his hands on in [[Marsember]], [[Cormyr]]. He was suspected to be a fence of stolen goods.
